Revision history for Perl extension Bitcoin::Crypto.

1.0
	- add extended private keys implementation with key derivation
	- add Bech32 segwit native addresses
	- move mnemonic handling to ExtPrivateKey (from PrivateKey)
	- rename Base58 functions to fix typo: from "perserve" to "preserve"
	- add new keys to Network configuration: extprv_version, extpub_version
	- basic private keys are now always left padded to 256 bit length (with \0)

0.02 Fri Nov 23 22:00:00 2018
	- enable package on ealier Perl versions
	- remove pack_hex from Bitcoin::Crypto::Util
	- add pad_hex to Bitoin::Crypto::Helpers

0.01  Mon Nov 15 21:58:51 2018
	- first version
